claude-onshape-mcp
==================

This project was started as a fork of https://github.com/hedless/onshape-mcp
at commit 54d21cc (2026), authored by hedless. The upstream project was
published publicly without a declared license; this redistribution is in
good faith and would be revoked on request.

Thanks to hedless for the initial scaffolding: the Onshape REST client
+ HMAC auth, the core BTMFeature-134 / BTMParameterQuantity-147 /
BTMIndividualQuery-138 payload builders, and the first pass at a
tool-per-primitive MCP surface.

Most of the product that exists today — truth-telling feedback,
multi-view rendering, entity discovery with outward normals,
parametric Variable Studios, FeatureScript custom-feature
orchestration, per-feature geometric diffs, the `hints:` rotation,
iterative agent harness via Claude Agent SDK, etc. — was built on top
of that scaffolding between April 16-17, 2026.

See `git log` for the full attribution trail. The first commit
(`vendor: initial import ...`) squashes the upstream history; every
subsequent commit is from this fork.
